    "actions_taken": [],
    "summary": "On August 3, 2019 at approximately 5:50 AM, the Motor Vessel Ms. Melissa, a 170 foot support vessel contracted by Fieldwood Energy, collided with the Bullwinkle platform in Green Canyon Block 65. The vessel damaged the starboard bow area and mast. The platform sustained damage to the Northwest walkway and bumper at the +10 level. No injuries were reported and safety systems and production equipment were not damaged.",
